      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "NEVER, EVER use <code>Mockito.any()</code> for attempting to verify exact values. This is a lazy test and does not verify the code is utilizing values that it&#39;s supposed to. It just verifies that you&#39;re using &#39;something&#39; which could be anything at all. Super bad test code. I&#39;m appalled at how many upvotes this has received."
