      "body" : "In my use case, I needed to match an array, of which it was not possible to know the order. I could not find a Mockito matcher which matched arrays <i>order agnostic</i>, for this case I found the <code>argThat(ArgumentMatcher&lt;int[]&gt;</code> worked well and didn&#39;t add much complexity."
