  "title" : "Mockito matcher and array of primitives",
  "body" : "<p>With Mockito, I want to <code>verify()</code> a method call with <code>byte[]</code> in its argument list, but I didn't find how to write this.</p>\n\n<pre><code> myMethod( byte[] )\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>I just want something like <code>anyByteArray()</code>, how to do that with Mockito ?</p>\n"
